@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ivrago(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.cos((v0 + 0.38 / v2 + 0.18)))
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.sin((v2 + 0.30 - v1 + 0.47)))
    v0 = (wp.exp(v2) / (wp.abs(tmp + 0.92) - 0.64))
    v1 = 0.19
    v1 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.61 / v0 + 0.86)) / wp.exp(wp.sin(v0 + 0.97)))
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.abs(v2 + 0.85)) - wp.abs((v0 + 0.45 - tmp + 0.93)))
    data[tid] = v0
